ARTICLE IX
 
"" means a consolidated, combined or unitary Tax Return that includes a Seller or any of its Affiliates (other than the Purchased Companies and their Subsidiaries), on the one hand, together with one or more Purchased Companies or Subsidiaries thereof, on the other hand.
