Combined Return
 
"" shall mean the affiliated group of corporations (within the meaning of Section 1504(a) without regard to the exclusions in Section 1504(b)(1) through (8) of the Code) of which a Tyco International Ltd. is the common parent (and any predecessor or successor to such affiliated group).
