.  Parent and each Seller agrees that, except with respect to the Restricted Areas in which the Excluded Businesses operate, from and after the date of this Agreement until three (3) years after the Closing Date (the "") it shall not, and it shall cause its Subsidiaries not to, directly or indirectly, in the Restricted Areas:
