"beneficial owner"
"beneficial ownership"
"option right"
 
right is exercisable immediately or only after the passage of time), directly or indirectly, of 25% or more of the equity securities of the Company entitled to vote for members of the board of directors or equivalent governing body of the Company on a partially-diluted basis (taking into account all such securities that such person or group has the right to acquire pursuant to any option right) (such percentage of equity securities being referred to herein as the ); that (i) if any Bank Credit Agreement Change in Control Provision contains a Threshold Percentage that is greater than 25%, the Threshold Percentage under this shall equal such greater percentage (but in no event to exceed 51% of the equity securities of the Company) and (ii) if the Bank Credit Agreement ceases altogether to contain a Bank Credit Agreement Change in Control Provision, the Threshold Percentage under this shall thereafter equal 51% of such voting equity securities of the Company.
