Section 2.1
                                     
Purchase and Sale of the Shares
.  Upon the terms and subject to the conditions of this Agreement, contemporaneously with the execution of this Agreement, the Sellers shall sell, assign, transfer, convey and deliver the Shares to the Buyer, free and clear of all Encumbrances, and the Buyer, in reliance on the representations, warranties and covenants of the Company contained herein, shall purchase the Shares from the Sellers, for the Purchase Price, payable as provided in Sections 2.2(b), 2.2(c) and 2.3.
 
