removed from any certificate of Parent Common Stock to be so transferred, to the extent permitted by federal securities laws.  The Parent agrees to promptly file an application for the listing of such shares of the Parent Common Stock on the New York Stock Exchange and to take all appropriate actions to cause such application to become effective as promptly as practicable.
 
