(b)
          
The Company shall be liable for all Obligations of the Designated Borrowers (irrespective of whether such Designated Borrowers are Domestic Subsidiaries or Foreign Subsidiaries) pursuant to the Company Guaranty.  The Obligations of the Company and each Designated Borrower that is a Domestic Subsidiary and not a Foreign Holding Company  shall be joint and several in nature.  Designated Borrowers that are Non-Excluded Foreign Subsidiaries shall be liable for the Obligations of all other Designated Borrowers that are Foreign Subsidiaries.  Designated Borrowers that are Excluded Foreign Subsidiaries or are Foreign Holding Companies shall have no liability for the Obligations of the Company or of any other Designated Borrowers.
 
