This Form 8-K/A is being filed as an amendment (the "Amendment") to the Current Report on Form 8-K filed by AECOM Technology Corporation (the "Company") with the Securities and Exchange Commission on March 9, 2011 (the "Original Filing").  The sole purpose of this Amendment is to disclose the Company's decision regarding how frequently it will conduct future stockholder advisory votes on executive compensation.  No other changes are being made to the Original Filing.
 
